ComicInfo.Title: Thunder in the Netherworld!; The Fateful Change!
ComicInfo.Summary:
Thunder in the Netherworld!: Thor does so much damage to Hades that Pluto gives in and releases Hercules from the contract. Tana Nile sends Jane away on a long journey from which, says Tana, she must never return.
The Fateful Change!: Thor defeats Harokin and discovers they are nearly identical in appearance. The Warriors Three free Asgard's defenders from Harokin's dungeons.
